*VT100*color9:     rgb:cf/a3/a9
! green
*VT100*color2:     rgb:66/82/5d
*VT100*color10:    rgb:ca/f7/bb
! brown/yellow
*VT100*color3:     rgb:96/91/76
*VT100*color11:    rgb:ff/f8/bc
! blue
